{
  "resourceType" : "CapabilityStatement",
  "id" : "GestionnaireCdL",
  "language" : "fr",
  "text" : {
    "status" : "extensions",
    "div" : "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CapabilityStatement GestionnaireCdL</b></p><a name=\"GestionnaireCdL\"> </a><a name=\"hcGestionnaireCdL\"> </a><h2 id=\"title\">CI-SIS Cahier-de-Liaison - GestionnaireCdL</h2><ul><li>Version du guide d'implémentation : 3.0.1 </li><li>Version de FHIR : 4.0.1 </li><li>Formats supportés : <code>application/fhir+xml</code>, <code>application/fhir+json</code></li><li>Publié sur : 2023-02-15 14:22:10+0100 </li><li>Publié par : ANS </li></ul><blockquote class=\"impl-note\"><p><strong>Note aux implémenteurs : capacités FHIR</strong></p><p>Toute capacité FHIR peut être 'autorisée' par le système sauf si elle est explicitement marquée comme 'SHALL NOT'. Quelques éléments sont marqués comme MAY dans le guide d'implémentation pour souligner leur pertinence potentielle pour le cas d'usage.</p></blockquote><h3 id=\"shallIGs\">DOIT prendre en charge les guides d’implémentation suivants.</h3><ul><li>http://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/ImplementationGuides/ans.fhir.fr.cdl</li></ul><h2 id=\"rest\">Capacités RESTful FHIR</h2><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h3 id=\"mode1\" class=\"panel-title\">Mode: <code>server</code></h3></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div><p>Système d'information ou composant de système d'information qui implémente le cahier de liaison</p>\n</div><div class=\"lead\"><em>Security</em></div><blockquote><div><p>L’ANS propose des référentiels dédiés à la politique de sécurité (la PGSSI-S\n) et des mécanismes de sécurisation sont définis dans les volets de la couche Transport du Cadre d’Interopérabilité des systèmes\nd’information de santé (CI-SIS)</p>\n</div></blockquote><div class=\"lead\"><em>Résumé des interactions au niveau du système</em></div><ul><li>Supporte le/la <code>transaction</code>Les interactions sont décrites comme suit :<div><p>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-bundle-creation-note</p>\n</div></li><li>Supporte le/la <code>transaction</code>Les interactions sont décrites comme suit :<div><p>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-bundle-maj-note</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div><h3 id=\"resourcesCap1\">Capacités par ressource/profil</h3><h4 id=\"resourcesSummary1\">Résumé</h4><p>Le tableau récapitulatif liste les ressources faisant partie de cette configuration, et pour chaque ressource, il liste :</p><ul><li>Les profils pertinents (le cas échéant)</li><li>Les interactions supportées par chaque ressource (<b><span class=\"bg-info\">R</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">S</span></b>earch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">U</span></b>pdate, and <b><span class=\"bg-info\">C</span></b>reate, are always shown, while <b><span class=\"bg-info\">VR</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">P</span></b>atch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">D</span></b>elete, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">I</span></b>nstance, or <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">T</span></b>les types sont seulement présents si au moins une des ressources les prend en charge.</li><li><span>Les paramètres de recherche (SearchParameters) requis, recommandés, optionnels (le cas échéant). </span></li><li>Les ressources liées activées pour <code>_include</code></li><li>Les autres ressources activées pour <code>_revinclude</code></li><li>Les opérations sur la ressource (le cas échéant)</li></ul><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Type de Ressource</b></th><th><b>Profil</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET d'une ressource (interaction read)\">R</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET de l'ensemble des ressources du type (interaction search)\">S</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PUT d'une nouvelle version de ressource (interaction update)\">U</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"POST d'une nouvelle ressource (interaction create)\">C</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"DELETE d'une nouvelle ressource (interaction delete)\">D</b></th><th><b title=\"Paramètres de recherche requis et recommandés\">Recherches</b></th><th><code><b>_include</b></code></th><th><code><b>_revinclude</b></code></th><th><b>Opérations</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#Bundle1-1\">Bundle</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-cdl-bundle-creation-note.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-bundle-creation-note|3.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Patient1-2\">Patient</a></td><td><a href=\"https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/2.0.1/StructureDefinition-fr-core-patient.html\">https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/fr-core-patient|2.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>identifier, family, given, name</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#RelatedPerson1-3\">RelatedPerson</a></td><td><a href=\"https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/2.0.1/StructureDefinition-fr-core-related-person.html\">https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/fr-core-related-person|2.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>identifier, name</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Practitioner1-4\">Practitioner</a></td><td><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-practitioner.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-practitioner|1.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>identifier, family, given, name</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Organization1-5\">Organization</a></td><td><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-organization.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-organization|1.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>identifier</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Device1-6\">Device</a></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html\">http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Device|4.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>identifier</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#DocumentReference1-7\">DocumentReference</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-cdl-document-reference.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/cdl/StructureDefinition/cdl-document-reference|3.0.1</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y<span title=\"MAY\">y?</span></td><td>date, type, security-label</td><td><code>DocumentReference.subject</code>, <code>DocumentReference.author</code></td><td/><td/></tr></tbody></table></div><hr/><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Bundle1-1\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Bundle</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profil système de base</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-cdl-bundle-creation-note.html\">Bundle de création d'une noteversion : 3.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>create</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Patient1-2\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Patient</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profil système de base</span><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/2.0.1/StructureDefinition-fr-core-patient.html\">FR Core Patient Profileversion : 2.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/patient.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Identifiant du patient</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/patient.html#search\">family</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Nom de famille du patient</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/patient.html#search\">given</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Prénom du patient</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/patient.html#search\">name</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Nom du patient</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\">\u00a0</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"RelatedPerson1-3\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>RelatedPerson</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profil système de base</span><br/><a href=\"https://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/2.0.1/StructureDefinition-fr-core-related-person.html\">FR Core Related Person Profileversion : 2.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/relatedperson.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Identifiant de la personne de confiance</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/relatedperson.html#search\">name</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Nom de la personne de confiance</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\">\u00a0</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Practitioner1-4\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Practitioner</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profil système de base</span><br/><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-practitioner.html\">AS Practitioner Profileversion : 1.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Identifiant du Praticien</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">family</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Nom de famille du patient</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">given</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Prénom du patient</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">name</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Nom du patient</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\">\u00a0</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Organization1-5\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Organization</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profil système de base</span><br/><a href=\"https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/1.0.1/StructureDefinition-as-organization.html\">AS Organization Profileversion : 1.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Identifiant de l'organisation</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\">\u00a0</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Device1-6\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Device</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profil système de base</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html\">Deviceversion : 4.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>, <code>create</code>, <code>update</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Identifiant de l'équipement</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\">\u00a0</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"DocumentReference1-7\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>DocumentReference</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profil système de base</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-cdl-document-reference.html\">DocumentReference Cahier de Liaisonversion : 3.0.1)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Conformité au Profil</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li><strong>MAY</strong> support <code>delete</code>.</li><li>Supporte <code>update</code>, <code>create</code>, <code>delete</code>, <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Paramètres de recherche</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformité</th><th>Paramètre</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">date</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>date de création de la note</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">type</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>type de la note</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">security-label</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>degré de restriction de l'audience de la note</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\">\u00a0</div></div></div></div></div></div>"
  },
